   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of the Technical Assistance Facility (TAF) is to support ARAF&#x2019;s investment strategy of building profitable, scaling, and socially responsible climate adaptive businesses that serve the base of the pyramid (BoP) markets, support greater gender integration through targeted technical assistance (TA) interventions and provide a financial return to ARAF and its investors. The TAF shall provide funding to the following types of TA projects: (1) Funding for Climate Adaptation Interventions, including gender specific initiatives, (2) BDS and Management/Employee Training projects, (3) Lean Data projects, and (4) TAF Support projects.</narrative>
